0:
”Alexa open four twenty”
”Start a short experience”

skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: four twenty
des: 420 is a one-of-a-kind experience. The skill is all about relaxing and having fun. You can enjoy a number of random experiences each time you invoke the skill. You can choose from a 'short' or 'long' experience. We recommend using this skill on devices with immersive sound.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
